column2: SELECT TOP # oiii_#_reqw_err as oir, h_beta_reqw_err as hbr, nii_#_reqw_err as nir, h_alpha_reqw_err as har, specObjID    FROM galSpecLine as p    JOIN ZooNoSpec AS zns ON p.specObjID = zns.specObjID    JOIN specObjID AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.specObjID WHERE oiii_#_reqw_err > # AND oiii_#_reqw/oiii_#_reqw_err > #
